OL,3,CAlmost two thirds of charities axe
OL,4,Cjobs and services over financial strain
OL,6,FAlmost two thirds of charities have
OL,7,Faxed workers and vital services as
OL,8,Fthey come under pressure from falling
OL,9,Fincome, staff burnout and declining
OL,10,Fpublic donations, according to new
OL,11,Fresearch.
OL,13,FThe vast majority have warned they are
OL,14,Fconsidering leaving their roles amid
OL,15,Fintense conditions in the sector,
OL,16,Fexperts at Rathbones have warned.
OL,18,FResearch by the investment specialists
OL,19,Ffound that 95% of executives in the
OL,20,Fsector are thinking about leaving.
