OL,3,CAlmost two thirds of charities axe
OL,4,Cjobs and services over financial strain
OL,6,FMost surveyed charities warned that
OL,7,Fthey expect the autumn budget to
OL,8,Fnegatively hit their organisation,
OL,9,Fwhile 87% already fear they cannot
OL,10,Fabsorb higher wage and National
OL,11,FInsurance costs which came into force
OL,12,Fearlier this year.
OL,14,FMr Pitt added: "UK charities are
OL,15,Fentering the Autumn Budget with
OL,16,Fgenuine concern.
