OL,3,CAlmost two thirds of charities axe
OL,4,Cjobs and services over financial strain
OL,6,F"Many are already navigating the
OL,7,Fpressures of reduced donations and
OL,8,Frising operational costs, including
OL,9,Fhigher minimum wages and employers'
OL,10,FNational Insurance contributions.
OL,12,F"With 70% of charities expecting
OL,13,Ffinancial impacts from the upcoming
OL,14,FBudget, there is real anxiety about
OL,15,Fhow potential tax rises and benefit
OL,16,Fcuts could affect their ability to
OL,17,Fdeliver vital services."
